OL,3,CInmates record an album at Jersey
OL,4,Cprison to give them 'hope'
OL,6,FInmates at HMP La Moye are working
OL,7,Fwith a music charity to write and
OL,8,Frecord an album.
OL,10,FIt's hoped the six-day project will
OL,11,Fhelp with their rehabilitation and
OL,12,Freduce the risk of re-offending.
OL,14,FTwo musicians from Finding Rhythms,
OL,15,FFred Harper and Thabo Mkwanazi, have
OL,16,Fbeen running the sessions with the
OL,17,Fsupport of ArtHouse Jersey, The Moving
OL,18,FArts Collective and the Government of
OL,19,FJersey.
