OL,3,CInmates record an album at Jersey
OL,4,Cprison to give them 'hope'
OL,6,FMr Mkwanazi said: "In La Moye it's
OL,7,Fbeen incredible, they've been
OL,8,Fvulnerable, they've been honest,
OL,9,Fthey've been introspective.
OL,11,F"What this says is you're a person who
OL,12,Fis capable of doing a bad thing and
OL,13,Fcapable of doing a good thing. Here is
OL,14,Fa good thing and here is evidence that
OL,15,Fyou did it."
OL,17,FMr Harper added that the project had
OL,18,Fprovided a welcome boost to
OL,19,Fparticipants' self-esteem.
