OL,3,CInmates record an album at Jersey
OL,4,Cprison to give them 'hope'
OL,6,FHe said: "(It) gives them the hope
OL,7,Fthat they can achieve something when
OL,8,Fthey're released."
OL,10,FOne participant said: "You have to ask
OL,11,Fyourself what as a community, what do
OL,12,Fwe want from our prison service?
OL,14,F"Do we want to punish people or do we
OL,15,Fwant to bring them back into the
OL,16,Fcommunity and make them feel valuable,
OL,17,Fand turn this into a really positive
OL,18,Fexperience which brings rewards to the
OL,19,Fcommunity in the future? I'd
OL,20,Fpersonally prefer the second."
